Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Onat-Bagacay Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Braulio Manikan Memorial Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 743
An Act Changing the Name of the Onat-Bagacay Elementary School in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, to Braulio Manikan Memorial Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Onat-Bagacay Elementary School located in the Municipality of Ibajay, Province of Aklan, is hereby changed to Braulio Manikan Memorial Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
